{"word":"G3353 - μέτοχος - métochos - met'-okh-os - Fellow","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">μέτοχος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">métochos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">met'-okh-os</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Fellow</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"கூட்டாளியான, தோழரான, பங்குள்ள - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"1. sharing in, partaking of"},{"paragraph":"2. a partner"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G3348 - μετέχω - metéchō - met-ekh'-o/3348\">G3348</a>; <i>participant</i>, that is, (as noun) a <i>sharer</i>; by implication an <i>associate:</i> - fellow, partaker, partner.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1777/1777\">G1777</a>, <a href=\"#/G2192/2192\">G2192</a>, <a href=\"#/G2722/2722\">G2722</a>, <a href=\"#/G3348/3348\">G3348</a>, <a href=\"#/G3353/3353\">G3353</a>, <a href=\"#/G472/472\">G472</a>, <a href=\"#/G568/568\">G568</a>"}]}